Text:
The Frontend Fresh Newsletter was created in February 6th 2023 and focuses send tips, tutorials, and projects straight to readers inboxes on a weekly basis.

In the newsletter, readers can expect content that covers:

- In-depth tutorials and technical articles on technologies and frameworks within the front-end engineering ecosystem.
- Strategies in breaking into the software engineering industry and tips on leveling up your seniority.
- Interesting news and the latest developments from the world of tech.

By being part of the newsletter, readers also have direct communication with the author (Hassan). They can reach out to the author on topics like the projects they're working on, skills they're trying to learn, or jobs they're applying for by simple replying to any of emails sent to them.
Shakeela lives in Bang, India. She plays cricket.
